16:31.350 --> 16:33.550
in the floor of
the Halifax club,

16:33.652 --> 16:37.988
which he thought was
the 90-foot stone.

16:38.090 --> 16:40.157
I don't know, but that's
what he told his son.

16:40.259 --> 16:42.092
Is the Halifax Club
still in operation?

