17:06.617 --> 17:08.050
It's worth tracking down anyway.

17:08.153 --> 17:09.453
- Let's go look.
- Yeah.

17:09.555 --> 17:11.988
- Joe, thank you for joining us.
- You're welcome.

17:12.090 --> 17:15.392
<i>Could Alex and the team
actually be within reach</i>

17:15.493 --> 17:17.961
<i>of locating one of the key clues</i>

17:18.063 --> 17:20.230
<i>in solving in the
Oak Island mystery?</i>

17:20.332 --> 17:22.132
All right guys,
let's go for a walk.

17:22.233 --> 17:23.633
Yeah.

