<i>Working with ground
penetrating radar experts,</i>

17:53.815 --> 17:56.148
<i>Matt Savelle and Luke Melanson</i>

17:56.250 --> 17:58.150
<i>from Canadian Seabed
Research Limited...</i>

17:58.252 --> 17:59.885
Right here's good.

17:59.987 --> 18:03.088
<i>Craig and Jack are hoping
to locate evidence</i>

18:03.191 --> 18:05.958
<i>of possible underground
flood tunnels,</i>

