You don't get an exact image
of what's down there,

20:35.910 --> 20:38.911
but you'll get what they
call a parabola.

20:39.013 --> 20:41.914
We're getting preliminary
results.

20:42.016 --> 20:44.750
Maybe it could be
wave action from

20:44.852 --> 20:47.119
200 years ago that
cut into there.

20:47.221 --> 20:50.289
But it's definitely something
we need to pursue.

20:52.760 --> 20:54.226
That was an interesting one.

