<i>Jack and the team have just
discovered evidence</i>

21:06.674 --> 21:09.975
<i>of manmade construction
at Smith's Cove?</i>

21:10.077 --> 21:11.977
We started getting good hits

21:12.079 --> 21:13.912
and it really looked like we
were seeing

21:14.015 --> 21:17.983
these spikey responses from
the ground penetrating radar.

21:18.085 --> 21:19.685
I felt it was very good
reflections.

21:19.787 --> 21:21.286
It was definitely seeing
some sort

21:21.389 --> 21:23.322
of gouge being cut in there.

21:23.424 --> 21:25.724
Just based on this, you know,

21:25.826 --> 21:28.794
I think I have an idea
where I would like us

21:28.896 --> 21:30.129
- to do an excavation.
- Yeah.

